    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit maintains peak volumetric efficiency via its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and delivered to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Crucially, this chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring structural rigidity and timing precision. The suspension retains factory-spec kinematics with no bushing deflection. A true mechanical masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
